import pandas
import datetime
import pytz

[8]:

now = datetime.datetime.now(tz=pytz.timezone("Asia/Kuala_Lumpur"))
json_file = f"../../data/{now:%Y-%m-%d}.json"

[9]:

data = pandas.read_json(json_file)
# remove duplicates
cleaned_data = data[~data.duplicated(subset="id")]
